# Available recipes:
#  - leech-default:
#      just download files to $DOWNLOADS_DIR, doesn't do anything else
#
#  - leech-transmission [HOST] [USERNAME] [PASSWORD]:
#      don't download file, add URL directly to transmission instead
#      transmission will download file and do all the magic
#      you need transmission-remote installed and web interface enabled
#      [HOST] optional, host name where transmission web is installed
#      [USERNAME] optional, username to use when adding URL to transmission
#      [PASSWORD] optionsl, password to use when adding URL to transmission
